-- Xolo - All-in-one online accounting service for freelancers in Spain
('Xolo', 'Tax/Accounting', 'All-in-one online accounting and tax service designed specifically for freelancers (autónomos) in Spain. Comprehensive digital platform covering invoicing, expense management, quarterly and annual tax filing (IVA, IRPF), and personal income tax returns (Renta). Services include free autónomo registration with Hacienda and Social Security (with 6-month commitment), VAT calculations, VeriFactu-compliant invoicing, and ROI/intra-community VAT registration for international clients. Expert team with 10+ years experience provides personalized support in English and Spanish. Four pricing tiers available: Lite (€15/mo) for self-managed accounting, Starter (€49/mo) for new freelancers, Global (€59/mo) for international clients, and Premium (€99/mo) with priority support and phone consulting. Serves 150,000+ freelancers from 160 countries with over €6 billion in invoices processed. Fully remote service available nationwide throughout Spain.', 'Online Service (Estonia-based, Spain operations)', 'Nationwide', 'Nationwide', NULL, 'ayuda@xolo.io', 'https://www.xolo.io/es-en', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
